//// Skill proposal types — the unit of agent-led skill evolution.
////
//// A `SkillProposal` captures a candidate new (or updated) skill that the
//// Remembrancer derived from a CBR pattern. Proposals flow through the
//// Promotion Safety Gate (deterministic pre-filter + D' scorer + rate
//// limit) and either become Active skills or are dropped, with the outcome
//// recorded in the per-day skills log.
////
//// This module is types-only — no I/O. The pattern detector
//// (`src/skills/pattern.gleam`) emits these; the proposal log
//// (`src/skills/proposal_log.gleam`) persists them; the gate (PR-D) acts
//// on them.

